ivardefs.name: class
ivardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issues by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a class of coverage such as a level of deductables or co-payment.

ivardefs.name: classDisplay
ivardefs.desc: A short description for the class.

ivardefs.name: group
ivardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify an employer group. May also be referred to as a Policy or Group ID.

ivardefs.name: groupDisplay
ivardefs.desc: A short description for the group.

ivardefs.name: plan
ivardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a collection of benefits provided to employees. May be referred to as a Section or Division ID.

ivardefs.name: planDisplay
ivardefs.desc: A short description for the plan.

ivardefs.name: subClass
ivardefs.desc: Identifies a sub-style or sub-collective of coverage issues by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subclass of coverage such as a sub-level of deductables or co-payment.

ivardefs.name: subClassDisplay
ivardefs.desc: A short description for the subclass.

ivardefs.name: subGroup
ivardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subset of an employer group.

ivardefs.name: subGroupDisplay
ivardefs.desc: A short description for the subgroup.

ivardefs.name: subPlan
ivardefs.desc: Identifies a sub-style or sub-collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subset of a collection of benefits provided to employees.

ivardefs.name: subPlanDisplay
ivardefs.desc: A short description for the subplan.

properties.desc: A suite of underwrite specific classifiers, for example may be used to identify a class of coverage or employer group, Policy, Plan.
